@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}- Laplace Manual ------------------------------------- About mice and men... -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}

@REM KEY 0 0 "Usage" "About mice and men..."
@{U}3.9) About mice and men...@{UU}

   You can use  the mouse to  change the active  entry or to  mark some  text,
thereby you can then make use of the @{"clipboard" LINK "Clipboard"}.

   If you make a double click on an entry, this has the same effect as  press-
ing return: The expression will be evaluated and the result is shown.


@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}------------------------------------------------------------------ ® by P!\K -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}
@ENDNODE
